FBIS4-29979 "dreas121_i_94007" FBIS-EAS-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 Cambodia Special Vietnamese Police Force Set Up Special Vietnamese Police Force Set Up BK2306033694 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 22 Jun 94 BK2306033694 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union Front of Cambodia Cambodian BFN [Excerpt] Diplomatic sources in Phnom Penh say the communist Vietnam has set up another special police force named F-91. This group closely operates with the Second Bureau of the two-headed government army. This Vietnamese special force commands and give orders to all puppet troops. It gives orders to Ke Kimyan, Pol Saroeun and other men in the General Staff office. There are also Vietnamese giving orders behind the back of Tie Banh in the National Defense Ministry. These sources also specify that it is this Vietnamese special force that carries out arrests and the most barbarous executions of people. [passage omitted]
